Not a particularly amusing response to a series of misogynist and racist quotes from the recipient of the presidential medal of honor winner Rush Limbaugh.
Blocked for being a jerk. But that is being mean to jerks.

Pres. Medal of Freedom Winner Rush Limbaugh on Hu Jintao, the former president of China speaking without a translator: "Hu Jintao was just going, Ching cha. Ching chang cho chow. Cha chow: Ching co. Chi ba ba ba." What the heck was @realdonaldtrump thinking? We know.

Presidential Medal of Freedom winner Rush Limbaugh on the idea of white guilt: "If any race of people should not have guilt about slavery, its Caucasians." What the hell was @realdondaltrump thinking and what does it say about his personal beliefs?

Prez Medal of Honor winner Rush Limbaugh on Sandra Fluke, who as a Georgetown law student in 2012 testified in support of Obama's birth control policies: "What does that make ? It makes her a slut, right? Makes her a prostitute." What were you thinking @realdonaldtrump

More of Medal of Honor winner Rush Limbaugh's disgusting quotes - on sexual consent: "If the left ever senses and smells that there's no consent in part of the equation, then here comes the rape police." What are you thinking @realdonaldtrump?

Here is what Pres. Medal of Honor Winner Rush Limbaugh said about the National Association for the Advancement of Color People: "The NAACP should have riot rehearsal. They should get a liquor store and practice robberies." @realdonaldtrump what the hell were you thinking?
@realdonaldtrump Presidential Medal of Freedom winner Rush Limbaugh on feminism: "Feminism was established so ugly broads can get access to the mainstream."

Here are some quotes from @realdonaldtrump Presidential recipient of the medal of freedom, Rush Limbaugh: "Holocaust? 90 million Indians. There is 4 million left. They have casinos, what is there to worry about?"
